<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.1.9">
<l>vaṇṭamarum vaṉamālai maṇimuṭimēl maṇanāṟu meṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>uṇṭivarpā laṉpeṉakkeṉ ṟorukālum pirikilē ṉeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>paṇṭivaraik kaṇṭaṟiva tevvūril yāmeṉṟē payilkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>kaṇṭavartam maṉamvaḻaṅkuṅ kaṇṇapurat tammāṉaik kaṇṭāḷ kollō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The forest garland, where bees linger, that is atop his jeweled crown</l>
<l rend="indent">wafts fragrance,”	she declares;</l>
<l>Saying, “I have [such] love for him,” “I cannot leave [him]</l>
<l rend="indent">for even a moment,” she declares;</l>
<l>“In what city was it that we knew [him], having seen him before?”</l>
<l rend="indent">she murmurs</l>
<l>Did she see the lord of Kaṇṇapuram</l>
<l rend="indent">where the minds of those who saw him remain?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
